{"tid":2053570,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"黃大仙民政處禁播《地厚天高》 稱「宣傳個人」違撥款指引 但曾批建國大業","createTime":"2020-06-06T11:34:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-02T05:55:24.000Z","uid":48083,"like":4,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b2bb7d477d3eb234c28ac9c0b6efd98b73557b5a","tid":2053570,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T11:34:44.000Z","msg":"（獨媒特約報導）影意志早前向黃大仙區議會申請2萬元撥款，舉辦三場街坊戲院，播放《地厚天高》、《亂世備忘》及《分域大道》，但遭黃大仙民政處駁回。<br />\n<br />\n民政處引用《區議會撥款指引》，指影意志申請撥款，並放映由其製作的電影屬利益衝突，和三套電影是以人物傳記或紀錄片形式，宣傳個別人士。影意志藝術總監崔允信回應獨媒查詢時稱，申請時沒有填寫電影名字，民政處及後曾主動詢問，遂提交電影名字，「其實2萬蚊唔係好多錢，係程序上有問題，議會批咗但你又返轉頭反對。」⋯⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n大埔區議會2018年曾撥款播《建國大業》<br />\n<br />\n對於過度讚揚的說法，崔允信不認同，稱據其理解，該條條例是用於防止區議員作個人宣傳，又指「傳記片就係宣傳個人？咁係咪藝術導演回顧又唔得呢？播唐滌生傳記俾阿婆睇又唔得？」他又翻查記錄，發現大埔區議會在2018年曾批出撥款，作放映《建國大業》。他質疑，「《建國大業》又係唔係宣傳共產黨嘅電影呢？當時嘅民政事務署點解唔阻止呢？」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1074247\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1074247&d=bCxsXTpKmrqj5N4FYztdx82proQWM4oxojYLcFbEfDU%3D&h=c074d055\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1074247&h=3fc33246\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1074247</a>"},{"pid":"ac2802da2c966f4be1268fbda33eb6108c69af28","tid":2053570,"uid":153151,"like":3,"dislike":7,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T11:34:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9Xz0C0n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9Xz0C0n.jpg&h=7b7d0741&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n誠懇呼籲唔好再舉美國旗，你唔係美國人又搞佢哋支旗，美國人會好反感<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/djateT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/djateT</a><br />\n#1 回覆 - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"65a6448b5e127f56183c17a2e4ce0f9b2bd22ff7","tid":2053570,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T12:58:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38d40638993802fba9d9ed23bca7692750b00b67","tid":2053570,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T13:26:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cd41ed0556ee37781a54634dea0846e539169f3","tid":2053570,"uid":14494,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T13:44:36.000Z","msg":"擺上區議會傾囉"},{"pid":"cd04c611a324ee24dc98f162896762e4250cfa63","tid":2053570,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0cd41ed0556ee37781a54634dea0846e539169f3","tid":2053570,"uid":14494,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T13:44:36.000Z","msg":"擺上區議會傾囉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T13:49:47.000Z","msg":"逼班狗官同少數派一齊睇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇完先有得討論"},{"pid":"4e2401323f3a0154f98976c1f2f441498766971d","tid":2053570,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T05:55:24.000Z","msg":"「後國安法時代」<br />\n《地》會變成禁片嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}